snippet.title: #WeAreWithYouAmberHeard : My Message to Amber
snippet.description:
This video is my message of encouraging support to Amber Heard in her time of personal crisis because she's been going through and what I want to say about what I've always seen in her and more importantly what I feel I see in the future for her, and that's something big and wonderful

Here's my written essay about Amber as well, the written companion piece to this video: https://www.quotev.com/OpenArmsPlayboyClubLives/journal/3188786/Bunny-Maureen-Miss-San-Antonio-the-Fiction-to-Reality-Search-for-Peace-What-Amber-Heard-Means-to-Me

Here are a few other sites/webpages I've done relating to Amber in  the past, with my support of The Playboy Club:
